{"tid":2487012,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[外流球員] 歐陽耀冲加盟J3球會YSCC橫濱","createTime":"2021-04-13T09:06:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T10:20:18.000Z","uid":9030,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"3c4f0ee4af71dd3b9fef6360dab6ec03c18fef87","tid":2487012,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:06:46.000Z","msg":"アオヨンユーチョン選手 Hong Kong Rangers Football Clubより完全移籍加入のお知らせ<br />\n<br />\nこの度、Hong Kong Rangers Football Clubよりアオヨンユーチョン選手が完全移籍加入することが決定しましたのでお知らせいたします。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmVAjqKTGxVqyUgHRUEBD6qydXvHCqKbLDt7aKZ5ncG1fy?filename=wFEmuh2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwFEmuh2.png&h=b95ac98a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e898674f66a531aaf83dfaa3a77aa5576fa7576","tid":2487012,"uid":140363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:08:14.000Z","msg":"隊波有幾多場比賽踢？"},{"pid":"48b44051034df441c35b04e6a929524991afb07a","tid":2487012,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e898674f66a531aaf83dfaa3a77aa5576fa7576","tid":2487012,"uid":140363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:08:14.000Z","msg":"隊波有幾多場比賽踢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:09:50.000Z","msg":"j3一季28場"},{"pid":"9a3a4dad2e2ce639db7c4abec9ab1f5b80faf034","tid":2487012,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:13:46.000Z","msg":"Au Yeung Yiu Chung （アオヨン ユーチョン）<br />\n【生年月日】1989年7月11日<br />\n【出身地】香港<br />\n【身長／体重】175cm／66kg<br />\n【ポジション】MF<br />\n<br />\n【サッカー歴】<br />\nHong Kong 09（香港） &ndash; Hong Kong 08（香港） &ndash; Workable Football Club（香港） &ndash; South China Athletic Association（香港） &ndash; Yokohama FC Hong Kong（香港） &ndash; Atl&eacute;tico Clube de Portugal（ポルトガル） - Grupo Sportivo de Loures（ポルトガル） &ndash; Guizhou Football Club（中国） &ndash; Dreams FC（香港） &ndash; Tai Po Football Club（香港） &ndash; Hong Kong Rangers Football Club（香港）<br />\n<br />\n【本人コメント】<br />\n子供の頃から日本でサッカーをするという夢。<br />\n遂にJリーガーになることができました。長年の夢が実現できました。<br />\nY.S.C.C.の皆様や協力していただいた関係者の皆様に心から感謝致します。<br />\n香港初のJリーガーとして、Y.S.C.C.の一員として、全身全霊をかけてJリーグの舞台で活躍し、チーム に貢献します。応援して頂ける皆様に恩返しをしたいと思います。これからも応援宜しくお願い致します。<br />\nEffort is always rewarded！<br />\n天道酬勤！"},{"pid":"87e1e67f4bc272a8fedfaf73d1944fd41d65abb4","tid":2487012,"uid":55468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:14:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://yscc1986.net/info/top-team/20210413001/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyscc1986.net%2Finfo%2Ftop-team%2F20210413001%2F&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11Ag0DHywPMniAnH04N%2BeXdM%3D&h=5d0ed6c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://yscc1986.net/info/top-team/20210413001/</a><br />\n官網都登咗"},{"pid":"9b638f26c3b7e6113698d18cb56b28e60cfefafc","tid":2487012,"uid":57035,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:16:40.000Z","msg":"Jleague個fb都出post歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmPnkuhQ6DK7NVtVsq1V6RtNAFDeGPUVyyY84ABSDM5mcz?filename=4hHbRz9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4hHbRz9.png&h=b290c7c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0525e94544f86e11269e6851c1a9d2057126b1d","tid":2487012,"uid":117894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:17:31.000Z","msg":"過左轉會窗都得？"},{"pid":"9f209c03c1d05bc30607b9b6cafad7742530a337","tid":2487012,"uid":163959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b0525e94544f86e11269e6851c1a9d2057126b1d","tid":2487012,"uid":117894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:17:31.000Z","msg":"過左轉會窗都得？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:18:26.000Z","msg":"轉會窗前搞掂轉會紙 <br />\n未公佈啫"},{"pid":"fd6e28b133e529574bda829124d51d271d6bf40f","tid":2487012,"uid":9030,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:18:44.000Z","msg":"歐沖:<br />\n我小時候就夢想著在日本踢足球。<br />\n最終我成為了J.League。長期的夢想實現了。<br />\n我們要對YSCC的每個人以及與我們合作的所有人表示由衷的感謝。<br />\n作為香港的第一個J聯賽，作為YSCC的成員，他將竭盡全力在J聯賽舞台上發揮作用，並為團隊做出貢獻。我想回饋支持我的每個人。我們期待您的繼續支持。<br />\n努力總是有回報的！<br />\n天道酬勤！"},{"pid":"b642773a0cd78372e98fc5fa302ab027e0f2b051","tid":2487012,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b638f26c3b7e6113698d18cb56b28e60cfefafc","tid":2487012,"uid":57035,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:16:40.000Z","msg":"Jleague個fb都出post歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4hHbRz9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4hHbRz9.png&h=b290c7c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:18:58.000Z","msg":"star<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427c1778f1f835fe83c04f2acf04644733d2b7c1","tid":2487012,"uid":111460,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:20:54.000Z","msg":"竟然係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f83c74b31854dcf655c2dcf2ce1615e01c56644f","tid":2487012,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T09:21:15.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;I have dreamed of playing soccer in Japan since I was a child.<br />\nFinally, I was able to become a J.League player. I was able to realize my dream of many years.<br />\nI would like to express my sincere gratitude to Y. S. C. C.  Yokohama and all the people who have helped me.<br />\nAs the first J.League player from Hong Kong and a member of Y. S. C. C. Yokohama, I will give my all to play in the J.League and contribute to the team.<br />\nI am grateful to everyone who supports me. I would like to return the favor to everyone who supports me. Thank you for your continuous support."},{"pid":"5457d869265a1e8f83dd2d872b4cdc0b5ec386fb","tid":2487012